# Test ROMs cloned locally for the `npm run test:roms` harness; not
# bundled — `npm run test:roms` auto-fetches the c-sp release zip on
# first run (set GLOWBOOT_NO_FETCH=1 to skip). TEST_ROMS.md lives
# alongside the corpus as our internal accuracy report and IS tracked.
tests/roms/
